<br>
I made my first reason not a personal preference because how tired I am of the reasons against GC, or Nintendo in general.  Many people have pointed out that the arguments against XBox are not any good, but I would like to point out that the same goes for the other systems too.  We just had someone simply say XBox is the the most powerful system, as if it is a measurable quality.<br>
<br>
He also had to make childish remarks about the name &quot;Dolphin&quot;.  One, it was a code-name.  All of the Nintendo systems have had code-names, which are never meant to be the final name.  Second, we already decided that the look of the system does not define the system, so the same should go for the name of the system.<br>
<br>
I already said why I like GC, its because I like the games.  Do you have any idea how many player hours I have on SSBM?  A few hundred, possibly the highest shelf life of any game I have ever played, except possible SSB!<br>
