<br>
the only things i see wrong with x-box, sure its a bit big and the controllers are big(thats why they have the controller-s) and it doesn't have as many games.<br>
<br>
oh and for a mere 50$ american's get x-box live (1 year) with a free x-box communicator(head set) thrown in.<br>
<br>
<br>
now just ask yourself one question, If I have the &quot;better sysem&quot; why am I complaining about the other ones? <p><br>
